{
  "id": "adv_event_2405_01_05_01",
  "title": "その覚悟は\n出来てる？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-producer001.m4a",
      "text": "撮影終了です！　みんな凄～く可愛くてかっこいい！\nこれぞLizNoir、って感じですね！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a wrap~! Everyone was so~ cute and cool!\nThat’s LizNoir for you!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 9.5066665173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6999997933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "スポンサーと打ち合わせを出来たおかげで\n相手側の要望もしっかり汲み取ることが出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to our meeting with the sponsor‚\nwe were able to get a good grasp of what they wanted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6999997933,
      "endTime": 15.3780272325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.5646937847
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "お力添え、ありがとうございました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5646937847,
      "endTime": 18.0749885082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-producer002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、頭を上げて下さい！　悪いのはこちらですし\nいいものを作りたいのは私だって同じですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ please lift your head! It’s our fault‚\nand I want to create something great‚ just like you all do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.268321832,
      "endTime": 26.474987157100003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6683204333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "出来るなら、最初からそうしてくれれば良かったのに\nまったく、今回は振り回されっぱなしだったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it was possible‚ I wish you had done that from the beginning.\nHonestly‚ we were just being jerked around this whole time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6683204333,
      "endTime": 34.234397475,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8131.679566699997
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10665.012899999998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.4349870999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-producer003.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、このたびは申し訳ありませんでした！！\nみなさんにはなんとお詫びを申し上げれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m truly sorry for what happened!!\nHow can I possibly apologize…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4349870999,
      "endTime": 42.1549847919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.3683181444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "わっ！　また見事なスライディング土下座！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! Another perfect sliding dogeza!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3683181444,
      "endTime": 45.559746615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.7597466627
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "さすが葵さん。弱点を責めるのに容赦がないですね～\nこころもまだまだ未熟です、葵さんを見習わないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of Aoi-san‚ she’s merciless when attacking weaknesses~.\nKokoro still has a lot to learn. I need to follow Aoi-san’s example.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7597466627,
      "endTime": 54.5500868955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7367536384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "土下座はやめてよ。もう怒ってないから\n……でも、少しくらいは文句を言ってもいいでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stop with the dogeza. I’m not angry anymore.\n…But it’s okay for me to complain a little‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7367536384,
      "endTime": 62.610993846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんね、葵\n貴方のことを振り回したのは、私も同じよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I’m sorry‚ Aoi.\nI was the one who dragged you around too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8034203051,
      "endTime": 67.96949725139999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.1561639467
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "お互いに、思ってることを言っただけでしょ\nただ……莉央、後で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We just said what we were thinking.\nBut… Rio‚ later――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1561639467,
      "endTime": 75.35806872040001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7299.9984740999935
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9123.836053299996
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9123.836053299996
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9010.502719999991
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.4561624208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "えーい！　莉央さんどぼーん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! Rio-san‚ splash!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4561624208,
      "endTime": 78.775436894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.9754369894
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "きゃっ？　私、今なんでプールに突き飛ばされたの！？\nこころ～、貴方って子は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyaa? Why was I just pushed into the pool!?\nKokoro~‚ you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9754369894,
      "endTime": 86.8384076276,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10655.260403900002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11771.229677200012
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11771.229677200012
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11657.896343900007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.0517407893
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、葵さんもごめんなさーい！\nえーい！　どぼーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I’m sorry‚ Aoi-san~!\nYay! Splash!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0517407893,
      "endTime": 91.49679751379999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.6306973933
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.703464047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ！？　なんで僕まで……まさか、頭を冷やせって\nこと？　あぁ……でも冷たくて気持ちいいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa!? Why me too… Don’t tell me‚ you want me to\ncool off? Ah… But it feels nice and cool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.703464047,
      "endTime": 103.8315365949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.0367973803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "お二人とも～、せっかくのプールなんですよ？\n無事撮影が終わったことですし、夏を楽しまないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ you two~. We’re at a pool!\nThe shoot is over‚ so we have to enjoy summer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.0367973803,
      "endTime": 112.4549156664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.6615824857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私も先輩達と一緒にプールで遊びたいなーって\n思って……つい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I wanted to play in the pool with you‚ seniors…\n…so I did…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6615824857,
      "endTime": 119.6520131269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.8520133176
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、突き飛ばしちゃってごめんなさ～い！\n調子に乗り過ぎました～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m sorry for pushing you~!\nI got a little carried away~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8520133176,
      "endTime": 124.9568205036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1701539514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、プロデューサーさん、ごめんなさい\n少しだけ、プールをお借りしてもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ producer-san‚ I’m sorry.\nWould it be alright if we borrowed the pool for a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1701539514,
      "endTime": 131.3898140428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プロデューサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Producer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2405_01_05-producer004.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！　このプールは撮影のために\n終日空けてありますし、撮影も終わりましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! We reserved this pool for the entire day\nfor the shoot‚ and we’re done now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.5764805951,
      "endTime": 137.856486813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
